    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Very large clocks, typically those that are a feature of city embellishment in important squares and buildings. In addition to the clock itself, the mechanism may include various animations, for example those having astonomical or animated figures.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
